data.description: Welcome Home to this fabulous 3 bedroom, 2 bath Pulte Home located in The Club at West Park. A highly desirable and sought after 55+ active adult community in the heart of Roseville! With over 1600 sq ft, this Nichols model offers an open floor plan with a large great room, high ceilings, gorgeous kitchen and beautifully landscaped backyard making this the perfect space for entertaining! The backyard features both a covered and uncovered patio, professionally landscaped, a very soothing water feature which creates the perfect space for sipping your coffee in the morning and enjoying the peaceful escape this backyard brings. The kitchen includes granite countertops, SS appliances, island with sink, dining bar and so much more! You won't want to miss everything this home has to offer!
